NOK: F21: 3.17.7-300.fc21.x86_64 on guest/host, qemu-kvm-2.1.2-7.fc21.x86_64 on host
NOK: F21: 3.17.8-300.fc21.x86_64 on guest/host, qemu-kvm-2.2.0-1.fc21.x86_64 on host
